&lt;gloss&gt;standard that is adopted by an international standardizing/standards
organization and made available to the public&lt;/gloss&gt;
&lt;ref&gt;ISO/IEC Guide 2:2004, definition 3.2.1.1&lt;/ref&gt;
&lt;/item&gt;
